Happy Birthday, my love. ♥️🫶🏻

Today isn’t just your birthday—  it’s a celebration of the amazing person you are and the beautiful journey we’ve shared together for the past 9 years.🙈 

From the moment we met, to the countless memories we’ve created, and now, sharing life as husband and wife—it’s been nothing short of a blessing. 💫🧿

You’ve been my rock, my peace, and my biggest joy.
I’m so proud of the man you are—kind, strong, loving, and real. And I’m endlessly grateful to call you mine.🥰

Here’s to more laughter, more adventures, and growing old together.
 May this year bring you all the happiness you’ve given me over the years—because you truly deserve it.

I love you more than words can ever capture. Happy Birthday, my forever person. ♥️♥️
